# ============================================================================
# NOTES
# ============================================================================

# This .gitignore file is optimized for the E-Commerce MERN stack project.
# Key exclusions:
# 1. node_modules/ - Dependencies (huge, should be installed fresh)
# 2. .env files - SECURITY CRITICAL (never commit sensitive data)
# 3. build/ dist/ - Compiled files (regenerated on build)
# 4. logs/ - Application logs
# 5. uploads/ - User uploaded files
# 6. IDE files - .vscode/, .idea/ (developer-specific)
# 7. OS files - .DS_Store, Thumbs.db
#
# SECURITY REMINDERS:
# - .env files must NEVER be committed
# - Use .env.example as template for configuration
# - Credentials should be in environment variables, not files
# - Review this .gitignore regularly
# - Keep .env.example updated with all needed keys (no actual values)

